$interpreted: Scared Soldier: Someone from the East Alliance once told me, that during the new year, a big monster would come out and eat people.

Bold Soldier: That sounds like a load of nonsense.
East Alliance is notorious for its many absurd folklores. Why would you believe all of them!
Puggi: Pang, go stand over there.
Puggi: HELP! SOS! The monster of East Alliance has appeared! The big, furry, and really ugly monster ARGHHH!
Puggi: Don't worry about me... Run... now.

Puggi: Leave the things in the cart, then... run... fast...
Do not look back...
Bold Soldier: T, there really is a monster!

Scared Soldier: A big, furry, and really ugly monster!!!!
HEEELLLPPPP!
Puggi: Pffft. Look at all this delicious food we got for pretty much nothing! Come, shower me with compliments and I shall share some with you~
Angelia: The food still hasn't arrived...
Dylan: We are short on time. I advise that we separate and search for food. Whether it's the marketplace or the lakeside, we'd search all possible locations.
Angelia: I'll let you guys handle this.

Naya: Not a problem.
We promised to let everyone have a happy new year after all!
